Directory structure
===================
   test_2d_gc_polar         -- executable
   gcsim2d_polar_input.nml  -- input file
   README                   -- info (this file)
   run/                     -- output directory
   gcsim2d_polar.gnu        -- gnuplot script
   gcsim2d_polar_ref.dat    -- reference results

HOWTO
=====
0. Create output directory if missing, and move into it
     $ mkdir run
     $ cd run

1. Run simulation within directory
     $ ../test_2d_gc_polar ../gcsim2d_polar_input

2. Run included gnuplot script
     $ gnuplot --persist ../gcsim2d_polar.gnu

3. Open *.xmf database with Visit (*)


(*) Make sure that the Xdmf plugin is installed!

